text: Wójtówka may refer to the following places in Poland: *Wójtówka, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Wójtówka, Gmina Bądkowo in Kuyavian- Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-central Poland) *Wójtówka, Gmina Waganiec in Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-central Poland) *Wójtówka, Masovian Voivodeship (east-central Poland)
title: Wójtówka
